title: Unleashed Universe - S001 Beast Wars
description:
NOTE: This is a Mash-Up series



Video = 8-9 [widescreen]



Audio = 9 [stereo]





The "Unleashed Universe" - where all the TV & Movie Universes meet.


**THE VISION!**

The aim and vision of this series is to -
remove the boundaries that separate our favorite stories from each other,
and to show how it is possible for them to co-exist,

therefor... allowing us the viewer, and indeed the story creators to not only merge,
but also to evolve the stories beyond any previous development - 
to allow the stories to become timeless and limitless. - 
This will be the biggest series in history, 
already 100's of episodes ready for the public.

**the story spans from the beginning of time, 
to the end of the Universe and time itself !**
